title: Work trade for rent
posting_body: ['Work Trade for a place to live', 'Work trade on a horse ranch (soquel)', 'Available soon...', 'I am looking for a single person or possible couple that is handy horse man or women.', 'You will need to have your own trailer, camper or motor home.', 'I have a beautiful ranch for you to enjoy being part of.', 'There is water, electrical hook ups, and septic disposal hook ups.', 'I want a work trade only...', 'You will need to do certain chores on the ranch.', 'Every morning and evening.', '365 days a year.', 'Including, but not limited to feeding, cleaning paddocks and stalls for horses.', 'Plus helping me with chores on the ranch.', 'Approx.', '3 hours a day.', 'You must be handy and able to drive a small tractor or willing to learn how.', 'I need someone that would be available everyday to feed the horses am and pm, clean for approx.', '10 to 14 horses daily, drag the arena when needed with my tractor and be handy with ranch work.', 'I can teach you all that you need to know and I will be on the property to help as well most of the time.', 'Someone Responsible Only!', 'No drugs, alcohol or smoking and due to other dogs on the property, no dogs!', 'There will be no pay.', 'You will get free housing in trade as the work necessary is truly less than 3 hours a day.', 'You will be responsible for all your necessary utilities.', 'Email if you are interested and want to live on a beautiful ranch with lots of beautiful animals.', 'You must be willing to commit to at least a year.']
